Package: landsatutils
Type: Package
Title: Implements Helpers for Common Landsat Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dewey Dunnington <dewey@fishandwhistle.net>
Maintainer: Dewey Dunnington <dewey@fishandwhistle.net>
Description: Acquiring, processing, and visualizing Landsat data is
  a common task. This package provides helper functions for workflows
  that are commonly implemented using these data.
